hotel-0.name: San Francisco Proper Hotel
hotel-0.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 5-minute walk of San Francisco Federal Building, Golden Gate Theatre, and Warfield Theater. United Nations Plaza and Orpheum Theater are also within 5 minutes.

hotel-1.name: Handlery Union Square Hotel
hotel-1.shortDescription: A half-block from cable cars, this hotel is 2 blocks from Westfield San Francisco Shopping Centre; the Moscone Center and the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art are 8 blocks away.

hotel-2.name: Parc 55 San Francisco - A Hilton Hotel
hotel-2.englishName: Parc 55 San Francisco - A Hilton Hotel
hotel-2.shortDescription: Just off Market Street, downtown San Francisco's major thoroughfare, this contemporary 32-story hotel is 1 block from San Francisco Centre shops and 3 blocks from the Moscone Convention Center.

hotel-3.name: White Swan Inn
hotel-3.shortDescription: The English-style inn is on San Francisco's Nob Hill, 2 blocks from a cable car line, 4 blocks from Union Square and Chinatown, and 1 mile from Moscone Center and the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art.

hotel-4.name: The Marker San Francisco, a Joie de Vivre Hotel
hotel-4.englishName: The Marker San Francisco, a Joie de Vivre Hotel
hotel-4.shortDescription: Eclectically decorated The Marker San Francisco, a 1910 Beaux Arts building, is within 2 blocks of Union Square and the Curran and ACT theaters. Moscone Convention Center is within a few blocks of the hotel.

hotel-5.name: Serrano Hotel
hotel-5.shortDescription: The Serrano Hotel is steps away from Union Square, perfectly positioned in the Theater District of San Francisco, 2 blocks from the Powell Street cable car.

hotel-6.name: Villa Florence San Francisco on Union Square
hotel-6.englishName: Villa Florence San Francisco on Union Square
hotel-6.shortDescription: Infused with the spirit of Italy, this romantic downtown San Francisco retreat is on the Powell Street cable car line, less than a block from Union Square; theaters and Market Street are two blocks away.

hotel-7.name: Grand Hyatt San Francisco Union Square
hotel-7.englishName: Grand Hyatt San Francisco Union Square
hotel-7.shortDescription: Rising 36 stories above Union Square, this sleek, contemporary hotel is 1 block from cable cars, 3 blocks from Westfield San Francisco Centre shopping mall, and 4 blocks from the Financial District.
hotel-7.roomRatePlanDescription: Standard Room, 2 Double Beds, City View - Bed and Breakfast

hotel-8.name: Axiom Hotel San Francisco
hotel-8.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 15-minute walk of Westfield San Francisco Centre, San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, and Asian Art Museum of San Francisco. Louise Davies Symphony Hall and TransAmerica Pyramid are also within 1 mi (2 km).

hotel-9.name: Hotel Nikko San Francisco
hotel-9.shortDescription: The Asian-inspired Hotel Nikko San Francisco is located downtown, a 4-minute walk from Union Square and the designer shops of Westfield San Francisco Centre. Guests can catch a cable car 2 blocks south, and both Curran Theatre and American Conservatory Theater are right around the corner.

hotel-10.name: Hyatt Regency San Francisco
hotel-10.shortDescription: The 17-story Hyatt Regency is located on the Embarcadero waterfront, across from the Ferry Building Marketplace, close to the Embarcadero Center, Union Square, and Moscone Convention Center.

hotel-11.name: The Westin St. Francis San Francisco on Union Square
hotel-11.englishName: The Westin St. Francis San Francisco on Union Square
hotel-11.shortDescription: This elegant and historic 1904 hotel offers a prime location across from San Francisco's Union Square; cable cars stop right at the front door, and the Financial District and Chinatown are both just 4 blocks away.
hotel-11.roomRatePlanDescription: Landmark Grand Deluxe King Room, Union Square View

hotel-12.name: Palace Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, San Francisco
hotel-12.englishName: Palace Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, San Francisco
hotel-12.shortDescription: A member of The Luxury Collection of Starwood Hotels and Resorts, this legendary 1909 hotel in downtown San Francisco is 1 block from the Financial District, 3 blocks from Union Square, and 4 blocks from Moscone Center.

hotel-13.name: Kimpton Sir Francis Drake Hotel
hotel-13.shortDescription: This 1928 hotel is a half-block from San Francisco's Union Square, 3 blocks from the theater district, and a half-mile from the Financial District and Moscone Center.

hotel-14.name: Executive Hotel Vintage Court
hotel-14.shortDescription: Executive Hotel Vintage Court places guests a 5-minute walk from Union Square shops like Tiffany & Co and Saks Fifth Avenue. Dim sum and Chinatown bargain shopping is 8 minutes away on foot. It’s a 20-minute cable-car ride to Fisherman's Wharf.

hotel-15.name: Hotel Zelos San Francisco
hotel-15.shortDescription: This downtown SoMa area Art Deco hotel nestles in the heart of San Francisco near Union Square, adjacent to the Westfield San Francisco Centre, Moscone Convention Center, and the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art.

hotel-16.name: InterContinental San Francisco
hotel-16.shortDescription: Opened in 2008, this downtown San Francisco hotel is adjacent to the Moscone Center and about 6 blocks from Union Square.

hotel-17.name: Hilton San Francisco Union Square
hotel-17.shortDescription: Iconic, AAA 4-Diamond hotel a few steps from Union Square, Cable Car station, theatre district, BART, Chinatown, SFMOMA, and Moscone Center. Upgraded rooms offer stunning views of the city and the Bay.

hotel-18.name: Marriott Courtyard San Francisco Downtown
hotel-18.shortDescription: This 18-story downtown San Francisco hotel is tucked away on a pleasantly quiet street in the SoMa (South of Market) district, 3 blocks from the Moscone Center and 4 blocks from baseball's AT&T Park.
hotel-18.roomRatePlanDescription: Room, 1 King Bed with Sofa bed, City View - Best Available

hotel-19.name: Holiday Inn San Francisco-Fisherman's Wharf
hotel-19.shortDescription: Located just 1 mile from Union Square, this Holiday Inn is within 2 blocks of Fisherman's Wharf and Ghirardelli Square.

hotel-20.name: Marriott San Francisco Fisherman's Wharf
hotel-20.shortDescription: Clattering cable cars, fun-filled Fisherman's Wharf, and the tasty temptations of Ghirardelli Square are within 2 blocks of this hotel; the Financial District and Union Square are less than 2 miles away.

hotel-21.name: Staypineapple at The Alise San Francisco
hotel-21.englishName: Staypineapple at The Alise San Francisco
hotel-21.shortDescription: Built in 1913, this handsomely updated boutique hotel is in the midst of San Francisco's Union Square district, 2 blocks from the Curran and ACT theaters, and 3 from the Golden Gate Theatre.

hotel-22.name: The Cartwright Hotel - Union Square BW Premier Collection
hotel-22.englishName: The Cartwright Hotel - Union Square BW Premier Collection
hotel-22.shortDescription: A half-block from the Powell Street cable car line, and within 2 blocks of Union Square, the Cartwright Hotel - Union Square BW Premier Collection is a quiet oasis on an otherwise busy block of downtown San Francisco.
hotel-22.roomRatePlanDescription: Standard Room, 1 King Bed, Non Smoking - Advanced Purchase

hotel-23.name: InterContinental Mark Hopkins
hotel-23.shortDescription: This San Francisco hotel sits atop Nob Hill, next to 3 cable car lines; Chinatown is 3 blocks away, and Union Square is 5 blocks away.

hotel-24.name: W San Francisco
hotel-24.shortDescription: Located in the trendy South of Market district (SoMa), the downtown hotel is adjacent to the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art (SFMOMA), across from the Moscone Center, and five blocks from Union Square.

hotel-25.name: Holiday Inn Express and Suites Fisherman's Wharf
hotel-25.englishName: Holiday Inn Express and Suites Fisherman's Wharf
hotel-25.shortDescription: This San Francisco hotel is within 2 blocks of Fisherman's Wharf and less than 2 miles from the Union Square District.

hotel-26.name: The Andrews Hotel
hotel-26.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 15-minute walk of Westfield San Francisco Centre and San Francisco Museum of Modern Art. Lombard Street and Asian Art Museum of San Francisco are also within 1 mi (2 km).

hotel-27.name: Sheraton Fisherman's Wharf Hotel
hotel-27.shortDescription: This smoke-free San Francisco Sheraton is within 2 blocks of the cable car turnaround and Pier 39, 5 blocks from Ghirardelli Square, and within 1 mile of Lombard Street and Chinatown.

hotel-28.name: Lombard Motor Inn
hotel-28.shortDescription: Situated on famous Lombard Street in San Francisco's Marina District, this budget hotel is less than 1 mile from Fisherman's Wharf, and 1.5 miles from the Palace of Fine Arts.

hotel-29.name: Hotel Zephyr
hotel-29.shortDescription: This family-friendly San Francisco hotel is located on the waterfront, within a 5-minute walk of Wax Museum at Fisherman's Wharf, Pier 39, and Ripley's Believe It Or Not Museum. Aquarium of the Bay and Ghirardelli Square are also within 15 minutes.

hotel-30.name: Orchard Garden Hotel
hotel-30.shortDescription: Orchard Garden Hotel is right next to San Francisco's Chinatown Gate, about a block from the Financial District, and 2 blocks from Union Square's world-class shopping.

hotel-31.name: Bay Landing San Francisco Airport Hotel
hotel-31.englishName: Bay Landing San Francisco Airport Hotel
hotel-31.shortDescription: Adjacent to San Francisco Bay, this hotel sits on a quiet strip across from a bayside park and jogging path, 1 mile from a BART station, and 3 miles from the San Francisco airport.

hotel-32.name: Holiday Inn Golden Gateway
hotel-32.shortDescription: This San Francisco hotel is less than 1 block from the end of the California St. cable-car line, which runs east-west. Union Square, the theater district, and Nob Hill are all about 0.8 mi away.
hotel-32.roomRatePlanDescription: Room, 2 Double Beds, Non Smoking - Advance Purchase Offers

hotel-33.name: Kensington Park Hotel
hotel-33.shortDescription: Built in a Spanish Gothic style, this boutique hotel on San Francisco's Powell Street Cable Car Line lies in the theater and shopping district, 3 blocks from the Curran and ACT theaters.

hotel-34.name: Kimpton Buchanan Hotel
hotel-34.shortDescription: This stylish, modern hotel is in San Francisco's Japantown, less than 2 miles from Chinatown and Union Square.

hotel-35.name: The Ritz-Carlton, San Francisco
hotel-35.shortDescription: This Nob Hill hotel is adjacent to the California Street Cable Car line, and just steps away from the Financial District and the heart of Union Square.

hotel-36.name: Hotel 32One
hotel-36.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 10-minute walk of Academy of Art University, San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, and Westfield San Francisco Centre. TransAmerica Pyramid and Coit Tower are also within 1 mi (2 km).

hotel-37.name: The Urban
hotel-37.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 10-minute walk of Academy of Art University, San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, and TransAmerica Pyramid. Westfield San Francisco Centre and Coit Tower are also within 1 mi (2 km).
hotel-37.roomRatePlanDescription: Room, 1 Twin Bed, Shared Bathroom (Extended Stay)

hotel-38.name: Motel Capri
hotel-38.shortDescription: Located in Cow Hollow, this motel is within 1 mi (2 km) of Fort Mason, Lombard Street, and Ghirardelli Square. Palace of Fine Arts and Pier 39 are also within 2 mi (3 km).

hotel-39.name: JW Marriott San Francisco Union Square
hotel-39.englishName: JW Marriott San Francisco Union Square
hotel-39.shortDescription: Located within 2 blocks of 4 theaters, this hotel is 1 block from Union Square and 4 blocks from the Financial District and a half-mile from the Moscone Center and San Francisco Museum of Modern Art.

hotel-40.name: Inn at the Opera
hotel-40.shortDescription: This San Francisco hotel is located in the performing arts district, across the street from the War Memorial Opera House, 1 block from San Francisco City Hall, and 1 mile from Union Square.

hotel-41.name: da Vinci Villa
hotel-41.shortDescription: da Vinci Villa is in the Russian Hill neighborhood, 1 mile from Fisherman's Wharf. It’s a 10-minute stroll to the hairpin turns of Lombard Street, and 10 minutes to the boutiques at Ghirardelli Square. For a tour of the famous prison, guests can take an 8-minute cab ride to Alcatraz Cruises.

hotel-42.name: Alexis Park Hotel
hotel-42.shortDescription: Located in Downtown San Francisco, this hotel is within a 10-minute walk of Great American Music Hall, Asian Art Museum of San Francisco, and Louise Davies Symphony Hall. Westfield San Francisco Centre and San Francisco Museum of Modern Art are also within 1 mi (2 km).

hotel-43.name: Casa Loma Hotel
hotel-43.shortDescription: Located in Western Addition, this hotel is within a 15-minute walk of Painted Ladies and Louise Davies Symphony Hall. University of San Francisco and Asian Art Museum of San Francisco are also within 2 mi (3 km).
hotel-43.roomRatePlanDescription: Standard Room, 1 Queen Bed, Shared Bathroom

hotel-44.name: The Park Central San Francisco
hotel-44.shortDescription: Located in the heart of the South of Market district (SoMa), The Park Central San Francisco is across from Yerba Buena Gardens and close to the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, the Ferry Building, Moscone Center, Union Square, Financial District, and Chinatown. The area also offers many restaurants and nightlife.

hotel-45.name: Queen Anne Hotel
hotel-45.shortDescription: This historic, Victorian-style hotel is located in the charming Pacific Heights neighborhood, 10 blocks from Union Square and Nob Hill.

hotel-46.name: Hotel Diva
hotel-46.shortDescription: This downtown San Francisco hotel is surrounded by shopping, restaurants and theaters, only 2 blocks from Union Square, and just a few blocks from Moscone Convention Center, Chinatown and the Embarcadero.

hotel-47.name: Comfort Inn by the Bay
hotel-47.shortDescription: This 11-story San Francisco hotel is 3 blocks from a cable-car stop, 6 blocks from Ghirardelli Square and Fisherman's Wharf, and within 2 miles of Union Square and Chinatown.
hotel-47.roomRatePlanDescription: Traditional Room, 1 Queen Bed, No View

hotel-48.name: Fairmont Heritage Place, Ghirardelli Square
hotel-48.shortDescription: This family-friendly San Francisco hotel is located in the historical district, just steps from San Francisco Maritime National Historical Park and Ghirardelli Square. Lombard Street and Pier 39 are also within 15 minutes.

hotel-49.name: Larkspur Landing South San Francisco - An All-Suite Hotel
hotel-49.englishName: Larkspur Landing South San Francisco - An All-Suite Hotel
hotel-49.shortDescription: This all-suite hotel is conveniently located on a quiet street in an office park in South San Francisco, less than 4 miles from San Francisco International Airport.
